<p>The couple were seen celebrating his birthday in Sydney in June.  </p>

<p>The Vogue Australia's fashion director and her filmmaker beau were joined by a bevy of famous pals, including Pip Edwards, Sneaky Sound System singer Connie Mitchell and Double Rainbouu designer Mikey Nolan for the festivities.</p>

<p>The A-list crew, accompanied by Joel's mother, Marianne Edgerton, headed out for an Italian feast at a restaurant in Sydney.</p>

